1 WHEREAS, Judge Batiste has demonstrated a steadfast commitment to civic
2 engagement and youth mentorship through initiatives such as Judges in the Classroom,
3 where he inspired students and strengthened public trust in the judicial system; and
4 WHEREAS, Judge Batiste is married to Barbara Thomas Batiste and is the proud
5 father of nine children; and
6 WHEREAS, Judge Batiste exemplifies the highest ideals of leadership and service;
7 he is truly deserving of recognition for his incredible career.
8 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
9 Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend the Honorable Judge Alvin Batiste, Jr., on
10 the occasion of his retirement from the Eighteenth Judicial District Court and does hereby
11 extend enduring appreciation for his exemplary service to the citizens of the state of
12 Louisiana.
